{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回写明末乱世与袁崇焕冤案的阴影，袁承志幼年身世由此展开。江湖人与朝廷纷争交错，父辈忠义和国难家仇成为他日后行侠、辨明大义的根源。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "向打",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那督",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "粤东客栈",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "店房靠山，山谷响应，只听得",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐顺着他手指看去，只见远处有一点火光，喜道：",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张康吓了一跳，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐眼见四下乌云欲合，颇有雨意，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们是过路客人，想在府上借宿一晚。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老头儿叹了口气，道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐大吃一惊，道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老头儿道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老头儿道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "官兵到山里来干么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不料又是一记耳光，那人骂道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老头儿道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老王道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另一个嘶哑的声音道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐一听口音，正是昨晚打人的那个老王。张康走上一步，道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他见这两人年幼好欺，想把他们吓跑。那知张康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另外几名公差也大叫：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "英雄救命！他们要谋财害命。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张康叫道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乘马客道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一名公差喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到底怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说到这里，跪下叫道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话可真？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乌龙扫地",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真强盗来啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快上马。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捉强盗哪！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小牧童望了张朝唐三人一眼，应道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那农夫向小路的一边指了一指，道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请出来吃饭吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人姓应。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那姓应的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓应的见他面色有异，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纪效新书",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓应的道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐心想：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心下佩服，说了声",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐大吃一惊，低问：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别看旁人隐私，只怕惹出祸来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐忙问：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "横架金梁",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回去！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "应大哥，你说怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张公子主仆放走，把姓杨的宰了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把招子废了",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓应的与众人对望了一眼，顿了一顿，对杨鹏举道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓应的道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举一拱手，转身要走。姓倪的突然站起来，厉声喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓朱的从桌下抽出一把利刃，轻轻倒掷过去。杨鹏举伸手接住，走近几步，左手平放桌上，飕的一刀，砍下两根手指，笑道：",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "山宗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人倒也古怪，怎么去了又回来。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐惊道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举见他们如此无礼，不禁大怒，喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当先那人喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "枯藤缠树",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨鹏举道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位一定也是去圣峰嶂了，咱们一路走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐更加摸不着头脑，不知",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧瞧去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐拱手说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐一揖进去，见桌上放着一本摊开手抄书本，一瞥之下，见写着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "千古奇冤",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张杨二人跟他出去。张康也想跟去，那人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "忠烈祠",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昏庸无道，不辨忠奸",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚愎自用，伤我元戎",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自坏神州万里长城，甘为炎黄苗裔罪人",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "功勋盖世则魏公遭毒，底定中土而青田受酖",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我督师威震宁远，歼彼巨酋",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "祭文读毕，赞礼的人唱道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_chong_huan",
      "speaker_name": "袁崇焕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张朝唐连称：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_chong_huan",
      "speaker_name": "袁崇焕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙仲寿命人拿过文房四宝来，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_chong_huan",
      "speaker_name": "袁崇焕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某某营某将军",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某某镇某总兵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓟镇副总兵朱安国",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 874,
      "line_end": 874
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙仲寿道：",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱安国道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙仲寿道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chong_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崇祯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个矮子站了起来，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 908,
      "line_end": 908
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙仲寿道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那矮子说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众人一听，都轰叫起来。孙仲寿道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 914
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赵参将道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "李自成",
